## OpenWrt opkg feed

Published builds are available as an opkg feed through GitHub Pages:

```sh
echo 'src/gz fluxproxy https://shallowhave.github.io/homeproxy/releases' >> /etc/opkg/customfeeds.conf
opkg update
opkg install luci-app-fluxproxy
```

